fields.title: 1.Choose Your Item
fields.content:
• Browse the available products on our website and select the item(s) you wish to purchase.
  • Add the item(s) to your cart and proceed to checkout.

fields.title: 2.Review Your Order
fields.content:
•  Check your cart to ensure that all selected items and quantities are correct.
  • Enter any discount codes or coupons if applicable.
  • Confirm the total amount due, including taxes and shipping (if any).

fields.title: 3.Select Payment Method
fields.content:
• Choose your preferred payment method from the available options: 

               -Tigo Pesa-  Lipa Namba.

                -Vodacom M-Pesa- Lipa Namba.

fields.title: 4.Make Payment
fields.content:
• Follow the instructions for your selected payment method:
  • Tigo Pesa:
    • Dial *150*01# on your Tigo phone.
    • Select the Pay Bill option.
    • Enter the Business Number and Account Number provided at checkout.
    • Enter the amount to be paid and follow the prompts to complete the payment.
  • Vodacom M-Pesa:
    • Dial *150*00# on your Vodacom phone.
    • Select Pay Bill.
    • Enter the Business Number and Account Number provided at checkout.
    • Enter the amount to be paid and confirm the payment.
  • Lipa Namba:
    • Dial *150*00# or use the Lipa Namba app.
    • Select Pay Bill or Purchase.
    • Enter the Business Number and Account Number provided at checkout.
    • Enter the amount to be paid and follow the prompts to complete the payment.

fields.title: 5.Confirm Payment
fields.content:
• Verify that you have received a payment confirmation SMS from your mobile payment provider.
  • Return to our website and confirm that the payment was successful.

fields.title: 6.Receive Confirmation
fields.content: • Check your email or SMS for an order confirmation with details of your purchase and estimated delivery time.

fields.title: 7.Wait for Delivery
fields.content:
• Track your order using the tracking number provided in your confirmation message
  • Receive your items at the address you provided during checkout..

fields.title: 8.Contact Support (if needed)
fields.content: • If you encounter any issues with your payment or order, please contact our customer support team for assistance.

fields.title: iphone 16 pro-max
fields.description:
The iPhone 16 Pro Max is Apple's latest flagship smartphone, designed to deliver a premium experience with cutting-edge technology. Featuring a stunning 6.7-inch ProMotion display with an ultra-high refresh rate, the iPhone 16 Pro Max offers an immersive visual experience with vibrant colors and deep blacks. Powered by the A18 Bionic chip, it ensures lightning-fast performance and efficiency, handling demanding tasks and graphics-intensive games with ease.

The device boasts a refined design with a durable ceramic shield front cover and a matte textured glass back, available in a range of sleek colors. Its advanced triple-camera system includes a 48MP main sensor, ultra-wide, and telephoto lenses, offering unparalleled photography capabilities, even in low light. The iPhone 16 Pro Max also introduces enhanced AI-driven features for photography and video, such as improved Night mode, ProRAW, and 8K video recording.

Battery life is extended, providing all-day usage on a single charge, and the device supports fast charging and MagSafe wireless charging. The iPhone 16 Pro Max is also 5G-enabled, ensuring faster download speeds and more reliable connections. With iOS 18, users enjoy a seamless and intuitive experience, complete with new personalization options and enhanced privacy features. This is the ultimate device for those seeking the pinnacle of smartphone innovation.
